                    text: "The D3EA powered the Genesis (DH, 2011–2016), Grandeur (HG, 2010–2016), and Santa Fe (DM, 2012–2018) in 3.0 CRDi guise. All applications are longitudinal, Euro 5-compliant, and exclusive to markets including Europe, Korea, and Australia.",
