          title: "Hyundai G4DG Engine Guide 2025 | Specs, Issues, Models",
          description: `Official technical database for Hyundai G4DG (1999–2005): verified specs, compatible models, common failure. Sources from Hyundai TIS, VCA, EU regulations.`,
