          title: "Hyundai G4DH Engine Guide 2025 | Specs, Issues, Models",
          description: `Official technical database for Hyundai G4DH (2010–2018): verified specs, compatible models, common failure. Sources from Hyundai TIS, VCA, EU regulations.`,
