                    text: "The G4EK is mechanically simple and durable if maintained properly. Its main risk is timing belt failure—critical in this interference engine. With timely belt changes (every 60,000 km) and regular oil service, many examples exceed 250,000 km. Distributor wear is common in neglected units but avoidable with proper ignition maintenance.",
