                    "@type": "Answer",
                    text: "Moderate for a turbo petrol. In a 2002 Coupe 2.0T, expect ~10.2 L/100km (city) and ~7.1 L/100km (highway), or ~33 mpg UK combined. Real-world economy depends heavily on driving style—aggressive use can exceed 12 L/100km.",
