                    text: "Yes. The G4EK-TC is an interference engine due to its SOHC valvetrain and tight piston-to-valve clearance. If the timing belt fails or jumps, valve-to-piston contact can cause severe internal damage. Strict adherence to the 60,000 km belt replacement interval is critical.",
