                    text: "The G4FG is generally reliable, especially post-2013 models with updated pistons. Early engines (2010–2013) may consume oil faster, but with proper maintenance—regular oil changes using 5W-30 and timely piston updates if needed—the engine can exceed 200,000 km without major issues.",
