                    text: "Hyundai specifies 5W‑30 synthetic or semi-synthetic oil meeting Hyundai SP or API SM/ILSAC GF‑4 standards. Always avoid ACEA A3/B4 or high-SAPS oils, which can accelerate HLA wear.",
