                    text: "The G4JS is generally robust when maintained properly, but early models (2000–2002) are prone to camshaft wear. Later revisions (post-2002) addressed this with improved metallurgy. Regular oil changes with API SJ/SH or better oil significantly extend engine life. With care, 250,000 km is achievable.",
