                    text: "The G4KC powers the i20 (PB, 2020–2024), Bayon (2021–2024), Kona (OS, 2020–2024), and Kia Stonic facelift (YB, 2021–2024). It is used exclusively in 1.5 MPi (not GDi) variants and complies with Euro 6d emissions across all applications.",
