                    "@type": "Answer",
                    text: "The G6BV is generally robust in hybrid applications, especially post-2014 models with updated cam phaser seals. Early engines (2011–2013) may develop VVT oil leaks if incorrect oil is used or changes are delayed. With proper maintenance using 0W‑20 oil and 10,000 km intervals, many examples exceed 200,000 km without major issues.",
