                    text: "The G6CT is generally smooth and durable with disciplined maintenance. Early models (2005–2007) are prone to HLA noise if oil changes are delayed, but post-2008 revisions improved reliability. Using correct 5W-30 oil and adhering to 10,000 km service intervals ensures longevity beyond 200,000 km.",
