                    "@type": "Answer",
                    text: "The G4LD is generally reliable with proper maintenance. Early models (2020–2021) had occasional 48‑V hybrid communication faults, addressed in 2022 software updates. With correct 0W‑20 oil, timely timing belt replacement, and software updates, examples are expected to exceed 200,000 km without major issues.",
